{"tid":1885824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會係咪派錢今晚利物浦對馬體會,利物浦客勝有2倍","createTime":"2020-02-18T14:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T23:40:22.000Z","uid":60916,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b951b9d1c287ae915ddf15ef488ff2bc3362aa","tid":1885824,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"今年馬體會廢到仆街<br />\n唔d咩祖奧菲力斯咩哥利亞高基莫拉達廢到不值一提<br />\n你睇下佢廢到咁<br />\n所以季中先要搵返中超都踢唔掂既卡拉斯高就知咩事<br />\n至於利物浦今年有幾勁就唔多講啦<br />\n英超差唔多場場都贏波<br />\n呢幾年利物浦前場咁屈機<br />\n贏波就梗架啦<br />\n文尼1球沙拿1球法明奴1球奧力治1球<br />\n輕鬆大炒馬體會<br />\n馬會開個2倍利物浦贏波派錢益街坊買口罩買廁紙<br />\n陣間我買夠500M<br />\n聽日瞓醒咁就有首期上樓"},{"pid":"b19242655358358fe99e26c58992ec95dccf32c7","tid":1885824,"uid":14241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"樓主好有大志<br />\n首期1000m嘅樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以透露下睇中咗咩樓"},{"pid":"42dab1ae863ebc657668403fcbbcb123fa4af584","tid":1885824,"uid":27482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:28:40.000Z","msg":"阿婆都識買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844728ce9a67d40b980e946d7aac66e9d7c85209","tid":1885824,"uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T20:14:59.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"036bf77d103e806b9b36266547d2d020fae3de4b","tid":1885824,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T20:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e65bc794b92f66c98f7cbfe4e14aaf1f448481","tid":1885824,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b19242655358358fe99e26c58992ec95dccf32c7","tid":1885824,"uid":14241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"樓主好有大志<br />\n首期1000m嘅樓<img src=\